        "TileImage": "$($repository 42e7d00a-b477-4c4f-8b13-8cd4e7403e0d).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47, this mission is a stranger one. Our contractor, the chief of the Sapienza police has tasked us with killing 5 members of the Sapienza Mafia. Matteo Arturi, the leader of the group has been trying to convince people to make him the leader, with his smaller group joining in. What the chief of police believes may make the Mafia start to break down is if this small group of planned defectors mysteriously died. Good luck, 47.",
